== 製作 ==
最初{{link-en|強·史派茲|Jon Spaihts}}所寫的劇本在好萊塢被列入2007年的{{link-en|黑名單 (電影製作)|Black List (survey)|黑名單}}，成為好萊塢難以達到[[綠燈_(電影製作)|綠燈]]標準的項目之一<ref name="EW">{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2016/08/12/passengers-chris-pratt-jennifer-lawrence-photos|title=Passengers: Jennifer Lawrence, Chris Pratt are out of this world in exclusive first photos|author=Sara Vilkomerson|work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=2016-08-12|accessdate=2016-08-13|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108130734/https://ew.com/article/2016/08/12/passengers-chris-pratt-jennifer-lawrence-photos/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Budget"/>，長期處於{{link-en|開發者地獄|Development hell}}<ref name="SheenCast"/>。在電影由[[索尼影視娛樂|索尼]]接手前，有一段時間是[[溫斯坦影業|溫斯坦影業]]所有，預算約3500萬美元，並打算讓[[基努·李維|基努·李維]]和[[瑞絲·薇斯朋|瑞絲·薇斯朋]]主演<ref name="Budget"/>。{{link-en|布萊恩·柯克|Brian Kirk}}曾被選作導演<ref>{{cite web|title=Keanu Reeves Sci-Fi Film ‘Passengers’ Gets a ‘Game of Thrones’ Director|url=http://screenrant.com/keanu-reeves-passengers-movie-game-thrones-director/|publisher=screenrant.com|accessdate=2013-07-16|archive-date=2016-05-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160530041607/http://screenrant.com/keanu-reeves-passengers-movie-game-thrones-director/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，由Wayfare Entertainment出資和製作<ref>{{cite news|title=Sci-Fi Pic ‘Passengers’ t Star Keanu Reeves, with Brian Kirk Directing and Wayfare Entertainment Producing|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/04/keanu-reeves-passengers-sci-fi-movie-casting/|accessdate=2013-07-16|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=2013-04-18|archive-date=2013-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029193336/http://www.deadline.com/2013/04/keanu-reeves-passengers-sci-fi-movie-casting/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年12月5日，宣布[[索尼影視娛樂|索尼影視娛樂]]已成功買下電影的版權<ref>{{cite news|last1=Fleming Jr|first1=Mike|title=Sony Wins Auction For Jon Spaihts Sci-Fi Script ‘Passengers’|url=http://deadline.com/2014/12/passengers-sony-pictures-jon-spaihts-1201311532/|accessdate